Get together. The bride in the center
and the groom over there.

01:55:27.320 --> 01:55:30.517
I've made up another poem
that goes like this:

01:55:30.680 --> 01:55:34.434
Though the world may be full
of beautiful things

01:55:34.720 --> 01:55:37.951
Full of towns that are attractive
Even more than this

01:55:38.120 --> 01:55:41.556
A drop of water will be good for you.
This way you'll get a bath.

01:55:41.720 --> 01:55:43.073
Get up!

01:55:44.000 --> 01:55:46.434
Is stopped raining, sit down.

