01:55:48.920 --> 01:55:52.549
- A wet bride is a lucky bride!
- Is the same sea, Ninola...

01:55:52.720 --> 01:55:56.315
...that stretches from here
to our Battipaglia, therefore:

01:55:56.480 --> 01:55:59.278
- Long live Italy!
- Long live Italy!

01:56:00.760 --> 01:56:02.990
Why, thank you!

01:56:03.280 --> 01:56:04.872
Thank you.

01:56:05.040 --> 01:56:08.316
How will you live

01:56:08.480 --> 01:56:11.074
So far away from our town?

01:56:12.440 --> 01:56:15.079
Goodbye to you all!
Go home! Bye!

01:56:16.720 --> 01:56:19.712
- Biscein bids you goodbye!
- I ate four bowls of soup...

01:56:19.880 --> 01:56:24.237
...two chickens, three pounds
of sausages and one candle.

01:56:25.520 --> 01:56:27.670
Naso!

01:56:28.720 --> 01:56:31.712
Naso, I'm going home!

01:56:33.280 --> 01:56:36.511
Wait for me. I'll come with you!

01:56:37.080 --> 01:56:38.911
Wait for me, you jerk!

01:56:58.960 --> 01:57:01.474
My bouquet! Wait!

01:57:01.840 --> 01:57:05.674
So long! I love you all!

01:57:07.720 --> 01:57:11.235
- Gradisca's going!
- She's leaving!

01:57:11.400 --> 01:57:14.312
- So long, Gradisca!
- Goodbye!

01:57:17.960 --> 01:57:21.475
- So long, Gradisca! So long!
- So long!

01:57:27.840 --> 01:57:29.353
Lallo...

